pmn01a-subtext: Murahawe ikaze mu rwaruka rwo mu rwaruka rwo mu rwaruka rw'i Ndera! Uyu munyeshure w'imyaka 10 n'amasegonda 24 y'amavuko, aratwereka uburyo bwo kwiyerekana n'urwaruka rufise imyaka iri hagati ya 10 na 24. Intumbero nyamukuru y'iryo higanwa ni ikibazo cuguruye: "Kugira amagara yanje arushirize kumera neza, ndabishaka." Abakiri bato bo hirya no hino kw'isi baravyishura, bituma babona ibintu bidasanzwe ku vyo bakeneye, icizigiro be n'ivyo bakeneye. Nurondere kumenya amakuru, urondere inkuru ziri inyuma y'ivyo biharuro, maze utwifatanye n'abandi mu kuremesha amajwi y'abakiri bato imiliyaridi 1.8 kw'isi yose. Kugira umenye vyinshi ku vyerekeye iryo hayanishwa, subiramwo http://www.1point8.org.
